      <title>小朋友, 你是否有很多问号?</title>
      <link href="/posts/f9398168/"/>
      <url>/posts/f9398168/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucas-nz/ImgHosting//img/%E5%B0%8F%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B,%E4%BD%A0%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E9%97%AE%E5%8F%B7.png" style="zoom:70%;" / loading="lazy"><gm-en><p>If we would have new Knowledge,</p><p>We would get a whole world of new questions.</p><a id="more"></a></gm-en><gm-cn><p>想要获得新知识, 就必须提出大量的问题.</p></gm-cn><ref><p> ——美国哲学家苏珊·兰格（Susanne Langer）</p><mark><p>摘抄自中国日报双语新闻公众号</p></mark></ref><blockquote><p>学而不思则罔,  思而不学则殆</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucas-nz/ImgHosting/img/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5%E5%8F%8C%E8%AF%AD%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%8F%B7.jpg" loading="lazy"></p>]]></content>
      
      
